Config
dotenv
Deployment
Any HTTPS-capable host (Railway, Render, VPS)

🌐 Deployment Tips
Your WEBHOOK_URL must be HTTPS — Telegram does not accept plain HTTP webhooks
Use a reverse proxy (nginx, Caddy) or a platform like Railway or Render that provides HTTPS automatically
Ensure your Firestore security rules restrict access appropriately
The /health endpoint can be used with uptime monitors like UptimeRobot

